<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 — Server Error</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
        background: #0d1117; color: #e6edf3;
        min-height: 100vh; display: flex;
        align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        padding: 24px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      .wrap { text-align: center; max-width: 420px; }
      .code {
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 6rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1;
        color: #21262d; letter-spacing: -4px;
        margin-bottom: 24px; user-select: none;
      }
      h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #8b949e; margin-bottom: 28px; line-height: 1.6; }
      .actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .btn {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
        padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500;
        text-decoration: none; transition: all .18s;
        font-family: inherit;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        background: #1f6feb; color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid rgba(88,166,255,.2);
      }
      .btn-primary:hover { background: #388bfd; }
      .btn-ghost {
        background: transparent; color: #8b949e;
        border: 1px solid #30363d;
      }
      .btn-ghost:hover { background: #161b22; color: #e6edf3; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="code">500</div>
      <h1>Something went wrong</h1>
      <p>
        An unexpected error occurred on the server. The issue has been noted.
        Please try again in a moment or return to the home page.
      </p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Back to home</a>
        <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-ghost">Go back</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
